title: ChatLLaMA - A Discord bot for chatting with Facebook's LLaMA language model. Have fun!
author: Nabakin
text:
4-5 days ago, I looked around and couldn't find a Discord bot to interact with LLaMA, so I made one! Since then, I've been adding features like embeds, slash commands, answer streaming, queuing, the ability to change the prompt, and more!

I built it on top of the extremely useful [text-generation-webui](https://github.com/oobabooga/text-generation-webui/) so if you already have that setup, it'll take like 2 minutes to run. If you just want to try it out and have fun, I've made a Discord server for it too https://discord.gg/TcRGDV754Y

Enjoy!
